== Major mode for editing Dos scripts (batch files) ==

This mode was renamed to BatMode which is part of core Emacs 24.4 and later.

The archived version of DosMode is useful for older versions of Emacs:

* Lisp:dos.el

The DosScripts page compares alternative Emacs modes available for editing Dos scripts, including Lisp:batch-mode.el and CmdMode.

Indentation for DosMode can be added with DosIndent

----
DosScripts
DosIndent
ProgrammingModes
